Xero has recently updated its API to deprecate broad scopes and replace them with precise granular scopes. Do NOT use deprecated scopes like 'accounting.transactions' or 'accounting.reports.read'. 
Instead, cross-reference the exact required granular scopes from the official page: https://developer.xero.com/documentation/guides/oauth2/scopes
(For example, use 'accounting.invoices', 'accounting.payments', 'accounting.contacts', etc., depending on the data needed below).

